<plot>The streetsweeper is a loner who finds poetry in the ordinary... The Streetsweeper is a languid off-beat 75 minute feature film. A portrait of an urban Australian landscape as seen through the keen eyes of an eccentric pedestrian: inspired by the great "street films" of Antonioni, Godard, Jarmusch, Kiarostami, Linklater, Tati, Vertov &amp; Wenders.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?518239</url></doc>
